APPRECIATIVE INQUIRY

Action planning using AI takes what you've learnt so far one step further. It helps you plan, prepare and reflect on your action.

Appreciative Inquiry

Appreciative Inquiry (AI) is all about the positive! It teaches us to focus on what's best about someone and the world around them on what's working rather than what isn't!

Keep it constructive.

Often people come at things from a problem perspective, rather than a positive one.

VS

Problem Solving

Appreciative Inquiry

PROBLEM SOLVING:

  • What to fix
  • Problems, symptoms and causes
  • Breaks things into pieces
  • Slow pace of change
  • Assumes there is a problem

APPRECIATIVE INQUIRY

  • What to grow
  • What is: working, better and possible
  • Focus on the 'big picture' ideal
  • Creates energy fast
  • Assumes infinite capacity
